			</footer><!-- .entry-meta -->
</article><!-- #post -->
							
<article id="post-655" class="post-655 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-geekery category-hackery category-programmery tag-application tag-connect tag-facebook tag-plugin tag-settings tag-sfc tag-simple-facebook-connect tag-wordpress">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
				<h1 class="entry-title">
			<a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/2010/how-to-setup-your-facebook-connect-application/" rel="bookmark">How to Setup your Facebook Connect Application</a>
		</h1>
		
		<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="date"><a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/2010/how-to-setup-your-facebook-connect-application/" title="Permalink to How to Setup your Facebook Connect Application" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2010-02-01T11:21:45+00:00">February 1, 2010</time></a></span><span class="categories-links"><a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/category/geekery/" title="View all posts in Geekery" rel="category tag">Geekery</a>, <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/category/geekery/hackery/" title="View all posts in Hackery" rel="category tag">Hackery</a>, <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/category/geekery/programmery/" title="View all posts in Programmery" rel="category tag">Programmery</a></span><span class="tags-links"><a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/tag/application/" rel="tag">application</a>, <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/tag/connect/" rel="tag">connect</a>, <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/tag/facebook/" rel="tag">facebook</a>, <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/tag/plugin/" rel="tag">plugin</a>, <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/tag/settings/" rel="tag">settings</a>, <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/tag/sfc/" rel="tag">sfc</a>, <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/tag/simple-facebook-connect/" rel="tag">simple facebook connect</a>, <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/tag/wordpress/" rel="tag">wordpress</a></span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/author/otto/" title="View all posts by Samuel “Otto” Wood" rel="author">Samuel “Otto” Wood</a></span>					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Note: This post has been moved to <a href="http://ottopress.com/2010/how-to-setup-your-facebook-connect-application/">here</a>. Please leave comments there instead.</p>
<p>The majority of the email I get from users of the <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/wordpress-plugins/simple-facebook-connect/">Simple Facebook Connect</a> plugin is questions regarding how to setup their Facebook Application. It&#8217;s really not that hard to do, but the plethora of options can seem  somewhat intimidating. So here&#8217;s the basics of what you need to do.</p>
<p> <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/2010/how-to-setup-your-facebook-connect-application/#more-655" class="more-link">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></p>
			</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
