<article id="post-603" class="post-603 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-general-spew category-linkery tag-facebook tag-idiots tag-phonebook tag-privacy tag-techcrunch">
	<header class="entry-header">
				<div class="entry-thumbnail">
			<img src="http://i0.wp.com/ottodestruct.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/facebook_logo2.png?resize=604%2C270" class="attachment-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Facebook Logo" data-attachment-id="611" data-orig-file="http://i2.wp.com/ottodestruct.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/facebook_logo2.png?resize=360%2C360" data-orig-size="360,360" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="Facebook Logo" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="http://i0.wp.com/ottodestruct.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/facebook_logo2.png?w=300" data-large-file="http://i0.wp.com/ottodestruct.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/facebook_logo2.png?w=1024" />		</div>
		
				<h1 class="entry-title">
			<a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/2009/facebook-phonebook-is-awesome/" rel="bookmark">Why I won&#039;t give you my phone number on Facebook</a>
		</h1>
		
		<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="date"><a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/2009/facebook-phonebook-is-awesome/" title="Permalink to Why I won&#039;t give you my phone number on Facebook" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2009-11-17T10:14:01+00:00">November 17, 2009</time></a></span><span class="categories-links"><a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/category/general-spew/" title="View all posts in General Spew" rel="category tag">General Spew</a>, <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/category/general-spew/linkery/" title="View all posts in Linkery" rel="category tag">Linkery</a></span><span class="tags-links"><a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/tag/facebook/" rel="tag">facebook</a>, <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/tag/idiots/" rel="tag">idiots</a>, <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/tag/phonebook/" rel="tag">phonebook</a>, <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/tag/privacy/" rel="tag">privacy</a>, <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/tag/techcrunch/" rel="tag">techcrunch</a></span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/author/otto/" title="View all posts by Samuel “Otto” Wood" rel="author">Samuel “Otto” Wood</a></span>					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Why won&#8217;t I give you my phone number on Facebook?</p>
<p>Because if you knew what you were doing, you wouldn&#8217;t need to ask me for it.</p>
<p>I was reading through my normal morning selection when I ran across this article on TechCrunch <a href="http://www.techcrunch.com/2009/11/16/lost-my-phone-give-me-your-number-groups-on-facebook-are-a-spammers-paradise/">detailing how they tricked a bunch of people</a> into giving up their phone number openly.</p>
<p>People, this is unnecessary. Why are you falling for this kind of nonsense?</p>
<p>If you lose your phone, here&#8217;s how to get those numbers back. More to the point, here&#8217;s how you can get your number to your friends *without* having them ask for it and without it being public knowledge.</p>
<p> <a href="http://ottodestruct.com/blog/2009/facebook-phonebook-is-awesome/#more-603" class="more-link">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></p>
			</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
	<footer class="entry-meta">
